address.streetAddress: The Diana A Plan, Sierra Vista

location.fullValue: The Diana A Plan, Sierra Vista

data.description: Stunning ANGLIA home in Sierra Vista subdivision, This lovely home is close to shopping, schools, and easy access to hwy 288, Only 5 years old with some recent updates which include, fresh paint, NEW laminate flooring in living, dinning & breakfast, Nice open concept from kitchen to living room, large kitchen island, granite countertops, all black applances, 42' maple cabinets with crown molding, undercabinet lighting, recess lighting, LED lighting,GE black on black appliance package, Ceiling fans in every room, Primary room is very spacious with large walk in closet, Primary bath has a standing shower and a garden tub, double sink vanity for his & her, 16 SEER HVAC System, Radiant barrier in attic, Double pane LOW-E Windows, PEX Plumbing, Good size 2nd and 3rd bedroom, Outside has a covered patio, large backyard, no back neighbors, HOME is still under 10yr structural builder warranty. Call me for more details, Must see to love!!
